context:
KR:
&lt;정신이 들어, 히스클리프?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Are you okay, Heathcliff?&gt;

KR:
&lt;달라.&gt;
EN:
&lt;No. You're not like him.&gt;

KR:
&lt;결국엔 돌아왔잖아, 너는.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Because you came back.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;…….&gt;

KR:
&lt;보장하진 못해. 그래도… 또 돌려놓을 거야.&gt;
EN:
&lt;If it happens again... I can't guarantee that I'll succeed, but I will try again.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그거야…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Well, that's...&gt;

KR:
&lt;너희들을 원래의 길로 돌려놓는 게 관리자인 내 역할이잖아.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Because I'm your manager. Bringing you back to your paths is what I do.&gt;
